Hey <%= @user.name%>!
<% if @numOfReviews == 0 %>
	Write your first review for <%= @assignment.title %>!
<% else %>
	<%= @numOfReviews %> MOOC-mates appreciate your help on <%= @assignment.title %>!
<% end%>

<% if !@reviewRequests.nil? %>
	Help <%if @numOfReviews ==0 %>your<%else%>other<% end %> MOOC-mates with some of their concerns:
	<% @reviewRequests.each do |r| %>
		"<%=r%>"
	<% end %>
<% end %>

Help your MOOC-mate out? <%= link_to assignment_url(@assignment)%>
Remember that you must give two MOOC-mates feedback before you can see your own, so helping your MOOC-mate helps you!
